    path: "../fig/image_place_holder.png"
  ),
  "table-18-6": (
    caption: [The three phases of *gastric secretion* (胃分泌): cephalic phase (脑相), gastric phase (胃相), and intestinal phase (肠相). Details the stimuli, mechanisms, and regulation of gastric acid and pepsin secretion during digestion.],
    path: "../fig/image_place_holder.png"
  ),
  "table-18-7": (
    caption: [Characteristics of the major *digestive enzymes* (消化酶). Comprehensive table listing enzymes from saliva, gastric juice, pancreatic juice, and brush border, including their substrates, products, and optimal pH conditions.],
    path: "../fig/image_place_holder.png"
  ),
  "table-18-8": (
